title: “Honeymoon in Vegas.” (Debate recap special!)
description: Jon, Jon, and Tommy break down the feistiest Democratic debate yet, hosted by NBC in Las Vegas, Nevada. Then Democratic candidate Jessica Cisneros talks to Tommy about her primary challenge to one of Congress's most conservative Democrats in Texas’s 28th district.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
